    "description": "从低温睡眠中醒来，你在一艘巨大的飞船上，你似乎是唯一的乘客。当你清醒过来时，你很快就会发现你突然觉醒的原因，并了解威胁到你的太空旅行宁静的危险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153690/extras/0632b1d689978a97579dac4737df2336.poster.avif?t=1729067860\" width=588 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153690/extras/0632b1d689978a97579dac4737df2336.webm?t=1729067860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153690/extras/0632b1d689978a97579dac4737df2336.mp4?t=1729067860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一个没有文字的宇宙</strong></h2><br>在一个神秘的谜题和谜语的世界中测试你的逻辑，没有文字或数字。没有无休止的对话或文字描述，世界是一个游乐场，一切都可以通过游戏来了解。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153690/extras/1033e818915fe7bf269f2d4e63a69813.poster.avif?t=1729067860\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153690/extras/1033e818915fe7bf269f2d4e63a69813.webm?t=1729067860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153690/extras/1033e818915fe7bf269f2d4e63a69813.mp4?t=1729067860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>生动的风景</strong></h2><br>无论你在哪里，总是有机器要操作，有工具要使用，有符号要破译。没有什么是随意放置的，每一个细节都可以帮助你。收集线索，揭开你过去的神秘面纱，并想办法逃离等待你的危险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153690/extras/9fa96221a53d84f66f159d6610d7177c.poster.avif?t=1729067860\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153690/extras/9fa96221a53d84f66f159d6610d7177c.webm?t=1729067860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153690/extras/9fa96221a53d84f66f159d6610d7177c.mp4?t=1729067860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一个令人惊讶的冒险</strong></h2><br>探索复古的像素艺术设置，迸发着色彩、互动物体和秘密。体验一次神话般的、不可预知的冒险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153690/extras/a747ef0d3d784c2e809b2cde95203b58.poster.avif?t=1729067860\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153690/extras/a747ef0d3d784c2e809b2cde95203b58.webm?t=1729067860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153690/extras/a747ef0d3d784c2e809b2cde95203b58.mp4?t=1729067860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
